{"id":91760,"title":"[Shoulder dislocation in athletes. Current therapy concepts].","abstract":"Shoulder dislocation is a common injury in athletes participating in contact and overhead sports. Optimal treatment is still a subject of controversial debate.Presentation of current concepts for therapy of shoulder dislocation in athletes.A selective literature search in PubMed was carried out.Surgical and non-surgical therapy options are described in the literature and can be successful in certain situations. A gold standard has yet to be defined.For decision-making numerous patient and sports-related factors need to be considered. There is a current trend towards early surgical stabilization in young athletes.","date":"2014-03-14","categories":"Wounds and Injuries","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24477426","annotations":[{"name":"Surgery","weight":0.553367,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Surgery"},{"name":"Therapy","weight":0.431257,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Therapy"},{"name":"Gold","weight":0.339972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gold"},{"name":"Injury","weight":0.317447,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Injury"},{"name":"Sport","weight":0.261381,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sport"},{"name":"Sportsperson","weight":0.18053,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sportsperson"},{"name":"Patient","weight":0.135792,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patient"},{"name":"Literature","weight":0.115637,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Literature"},{"name":"Shoulder","weight":0.11349,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shoulder"},{"name":"Debate","weight":0.0391252,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Debate"},{"name":"Controversy","weight":0.0370044,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Controversy"},{"name":"Gold standard","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gold_standard"},{"name":"PubMed","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/PubMed"},{"name":"Dislocated shoulder","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dislocated_shoulder"},{"name":"Reference counting","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Reference_counting"},{"name":"Standardization","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Standardization"},{"name":"Option (finance)","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Option_(finance)"},{"name":"Dislocation","weight":0.0152478,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dislocation"},{"name":"Natural selection","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Natural_selection"}]}
